[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "それじゃあイザナちゃん、私は部室に戻るね。\nレッスン頑張ってね！　応援してる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00133",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ありがとう！　レスナちゃんも頑張ってね！\nまた会いに行くね～！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00134",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "では改めてイザナ殿！　これから同じユニットの\nメンバーとして、よろしくお願いしまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00135",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "イザナでいいよ！\nこちらこそよろしくね、鬼門！　ヨハナ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00136",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "よろしく。\n……ねぇ、社長は？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00137",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "予定があるらしく、先ほど出て行かれました。\nレッスンを続けていてほしいとのことでございまする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00138",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "まずは、イザナの歌とダンスを見せてほしいでござる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00139",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うん、分かった！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00140",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "――ふぅ。どうだった？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00141",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "素人同然ね。\n勢いだけでアイドルを始めたのが分かるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00142",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "歌は置いておいても、ダンスはいいと思いまする！\nオリジナルの振り付けにセンスを感じまする……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00143",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "あんた、筋肉量と体幹はあるわね。\n何かやってるわけ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00144",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うーんと、もしかしたら、\n実家の鍛冶屋のお手伝いで鍛えられているのかも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00145",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "昔から、重いものを運んだり、\nハンマーを振って遊んだりしてるんだ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00146",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ぶんぶん！　ハンマー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00147",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "おおっ！　これは印象に残るいいアピールですな！\nパフォーマンスに使えそうでございまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00148",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "あんた、いつもこんなおっきいハンマー\n持ち歩いてるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00149",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うん！　これの他にも色んなハンマーを持ってるよ！\n気分によって持ち替えてるんだ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00150",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……あ、そう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00151",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "戻りましたわ。\nあなたたち！　今から大事な発表をしますわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00152",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "なんでございますか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00153",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなたたちの１ｓｔライブの日程が決まりましたわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00154",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ラ、ライブ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00155",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……随分急ね。ま、問題ないけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00156",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "して、日程はいつなのでございますか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00157",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "１ｓｔライブの日程は――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00158",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "明日ですわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00159",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "あ、明日ーっ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00160",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]